Name: scrollbar

Details:

Syntax:

Types:

Function:
`Figure scrollbar(Figure f, FProperty props ...)`

Synopsis:

Description:

Embed figure `f` in a horizontal and a vertical scrollbar.

Use [hscrollbar] or [vscrollbar] to add a scrollbar in only one dimension.

Examples:

<figure s1.png 400x400>
box1 = box(size(200,100), fillColor("Blue"));
render(scrollbar(box1));
</figure>
